Returns:

GObject_EqualsMethod 
typedef bool (*GObject_EqualsMethod)(GObject o1, GObject o2);
Equals method.

Parameters:
o1 - A GObject structure pointer.
o2 - A GObject structure pointer.
Returns:
True if the two objects are equal, otherwise False.
